For those of you who follow the IASSIST Interest Group on Human Subjects Review Committees and Privacy and Confidentiality in Research, you might be interested in this webinar:
Amy Pienta and Kaye Marz of ICPSR&rsquo;s National Addiction and HIV Data Archive Program will present a webinar on Nov. 28 titled &ldquo;Navigating Your IRB to Share Research Data.&rdquo;
They will share guidelines for working with Institutional Review Boards to release data that may contain sensitive information, such as studies on substance abuse.
